column5: Howey Bay froze over last night. Open water Fishing Season officially over for 2008. for pictures go to http://viking-island.blogspot.com/https://www.walleyecentral.com/forums...hp?albumid=108

Thanks for your blog. I've checked it every day, starting back in early May and I've alerted many of my fishing friends to take a look. Being able to follow what's happening in the Red Lake area makes my life better.Thanks.
Skidoos have been racing up and down the bay since Sunday November 23. (A few years ago, i went kayaking on the bay on November 21, but that was highly unusual)
